{
  "name": "Lemon Protein Cookies",
  "description": "Crumbl-style lemon protein cookie with a powdered-monk-fruit lemon drizzle. FLAGGED FOR TUNING: drizzle flavor underwhelming and macro profile (~13.4 cal/g protein) weaker than target - candidate for future versions (boost protein density, rework the drizzle). Quantities stored in grams (ugly cup measures converted). Standalone root; sweetener is maltodextrin-based granulated Splenda; drizzle monk fruit counted as 0 cal.",
